le_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">824</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg007.perseus-grc1:445\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hec.\">Hec.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">445</biblScope> </bibl>), but very rare in trim., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg002.perseus-grc1:297\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pers.\">Pers.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">297</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg002.perseus-grc1:762\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">762</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg007.perseus-grc1:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eu.\">Eu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1024\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1024</biblScope> </bibl> ; and in Prose only in special forms, such as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἅτε, ἐφ᾽ ᾧτε</foreign> :—rarely with antec. expressed, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θεάων τάων, αἵ τ᾽</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:332\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.332</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῷ ἴκελος, ὅν τ᾽</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24:758\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.758</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τά τε φρονέων, ἅ τ᾽ ἐγώπερ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:7:312\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.312</biblScope></bibl></cit>.—Not to be confounded with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅς τε,</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">and who,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:365\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.365</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:185\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.185</biblScope></bibl>,al. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n75588.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐξ οὗτε</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">from the</tr_> <pb n=\"1263\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">time when</tr_>. . , <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg002.perseus-grc1:762\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pers.\">Pers.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">762</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg007.perseus-grc1:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eu.\">Eu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀπ᾽ οὗτε</quote_> <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Cair.Zen.:291:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PCair.Zen.\">PCair.Zen.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">291.3</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B. C.)</date>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n75588.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> freq. folld. by <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">περ</itype><cit TEIform=\"cit\"><quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">, τά τε στυγέουσι θεοίπερ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:65\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.65</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n75588.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥα</foreign> between <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅς</foreign> and <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">τε</itype><foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">, αἴγειρος ὥς, ἥ ῥά τε</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:483\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.483</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:411\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.411</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:31\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.31</biblScope></bibl>, al. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n75588.4\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅ τε</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in that, because</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:244\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.244</biblScope> </bibl>; introducing the reason for making a statement or asking a question, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.32</biblScope></bibl>, al.; so prob. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:468\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.468</biblScope> </bibl>: for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἅτε, ᾧτε</foreign>, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> sub vocc.: <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ᾇτε</foreign>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dor.\">Dor.</a></gram> </gramGrp> for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ᾗτε</foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">as</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1308\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1308</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.): <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐφ᾽ ᾧτε</foreign>, <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἐπί</ref> </xr> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">111.3</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}